'''Brian Turner''' is a patient who came into the ER at [[Seattle Grace Mercy West Hospital]].

==History==
While cleaning his gutters, Brian fell off the ladder and hit his head. He was taken to the ER at [[Seattle Grace Mercy West Hospital]]. He did not lose consciousness after his fall.

==Notes and Trivia==
*He was 55 at the time of his hospitalization.
